text: Ayukashevo () is a rural locality (a village) in Uchpilinsky Selsoviet, Dyurtyulinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 200 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 12 km from Dyurtyuli, 1 km from Uchpli. == References == Category:Rural localities in Dyurtyulinsky District
title: Ayukashevo
